;CYCLOSPORIN IS A CYCLIC UNDECAPEPTIDE. CYCLIZATION IS ACHIEVED BY LINKING THE N- AND THE C- TERMINI. THE CYCLOSPORIN MOLECULE WAS MODIFIED AT POSITION 8 TO BE 4,N-DIMETHYLNORLEUCINE.
;
